Definition: heart surgery in which the rib cage is spread open, the heart is stopped and blood is detoured through a heart-lung machine while a heart valve or coronary artery is surgically repaired
Synonyms: heart_surgery, heart, surgery, in, which, the, rib, cage, is, spread, open, stopped, and, blood, detoured, through, a, heart-lung, machine, while, valve, or, coronary, artery, surgically, repaired
Category: noun.act
